defaultWritten evidence from the 
defaultChartered Institution of Highways and Transportation (CIHT) (SRN 035)
default&#xa0;
defaultCIHT is a membership organisation representing over 12,000 people who work in the highways and transportation sector.  CIHT members plan, design, build, operate and maintain best-in-class transport systems 
defaultand infrastructure, whilst respecting the imperatives of improving safety, ensuring economic competitiveness and minimising environmental impact.
default&#xa0;
defaultCIHT welcomes the opportunity to submit evidence to the Transport
default Select Committee
default’
defaults
default consultation on 
defaultthe Stra
defaulttegic Road network
default. 
defaultThis response incorporates the views of CIHT’s Council which 
defaultis a 
defaultrepresent
defaultative body of our members
default’
default interests and opinions
default. We would welcome the opportunity to expand upon our response as required.
