defaulte development of the network is fundamental to real and lasting improvements in the network. The role of a “regulator” acting in customers interests is commonplace in other sectors and in the transport sector and should be introduced alongside changes to t
defaulthe form of the Highways Agency in the way it manages the network. We set out in our response to Question 3 below how the requirements of customers should be 
